name: Portland Street Climb
description:
This week we will head to the hills and climb Portland St. making our way to Manor Park and then through the trail by Oat Hill Lake. After the lake we will shoot down Lorne Ave to Sinclair and make our way back to the Gazebo via Prince Albert along Lake Banook.
As always, we meet at the Sullivans Pond Gazebo at 6:30pm.
